messages: Every time I see one of my high school teachers out in public, I can't help but think of Janis Ian's quote in Mean Girls...
But then I remember that I like doing whatever the fuck I want right now too much to have a kid anytime soon and I forgot about it.
"Why is redbull and vodka so strange? I feel like I'm getting drunk and electrocuted at the same time." 😂
